      "key_findings": "Confirmed presence of alloy phases (ferrite, austenite, beta-Mn) in specimens oxidized at 800°C and in quenched specimens. Revealed scale structures and alloy phase boundaries."
    },
    {
      "characterization_id": "char_03",
