      "purpose": "Quantitative and qualitative composition analysis of scale cross-sections and elemental distribution maps",
      "key_findings": "Revealed high manganese concentrations in scales on high-Mn alloys; aluminum rich phases at alloy interface; Fe2O3 progressively disappeared in alloys containing more than 20% manganese. Two-layered scales at 1000°C composed almost entirely of Mn and Al oxides."
    },
